      # Proposal (Goal-Level)
      ## Outcomes
      - <what success looks like; measurable>
      ## In-Scope
      - <deliverables list>
      ## Out-of-Scope
      - <explicit exclusions to prevent scope creep>
      ## Timeline & Milestones
      - <phases with acceptance gates>
      ## Pricing
      - <reference to ratecard; package or T&M>
      ## Next Steps
      - <clarifications needed; start conditions>
